snippet.title: Freya Skye - golden boy
snippet.description:
Freya Skye "stardust" EP OUT NOW 

Listen/download here
Amazon: http://music.amazon.com/albums/B0GK5LXNPM?trackAsin=B0GK5HF392
Apple: https://apple.co/4q6KRvM
Itunes: https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/Title/1872542998?ls=1&app=itunes&at=1010lKkZ
Spotify: https://open.spotify.com/album/2HNjUP7VDUpyxQ2J3Cbch4
YouTube Music: https://music.youtube.com/playlist?list=OLAK5uy_lUnvU60mxdl8LaYe1G6axRe83BVASzkUs
 
D/P: Michel Borden

Subscribe to my YouTube channel: https://www.youtube.com/@iamfreyaskye 
Follow me on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/freyaskye
Follow me on Tiktok: https://tiktok.com/@freya

Lyrics to “golden boy” 

There was trail of destruction 
That led straight to you 
Ignored all the signs
That I wish weren’t true
You’re such a good actor
I guess you had me fooled
 
Guess I was convenient
When I was around
Cuz you love attention
The talk of the town
And I’d build you up
While you’d just tear me down
 
What’s done is done 
I’m on the other side now
 
So you can play the golden boy
And lose yourself in all the noise of
“You’re kind, and you’re so perfect” 
“I’d love to be your girlfriend”
You were lucky once
How’s life living on the surface?
 
We’d talk all the time
Now we don’t even speak 
I’m wide awake 
While you’re both still asleep 
You’re so unaffected 
By our history
 
But what’s done is done 
I’m on the other side now
 
So you can play the golden boy
And lose yourself in all the noise of
“You’re kind, and you’re so perfect” 
“I’d love to be your girlfriend”
You were lucky once
How’s life living on the surface?
 
You can really play the part
While you stay breaking all these hearts 
Oh “what’s it like to be his girlfriend”
Looks good but it’s a burden
You were lucky once
Have fun living on the surface
 
I’m thankful
You’re no longer wasting my time
I’m grateful I gave up
On reading your mind 
I know that it’s much better
Ending like this
Just one on your list 
Deceived and dismissed  
No I’m not alone being left in your mess 
It should bring me closure, or something I guess 
But all that I’m left with are unproven words 
That everyone heard, and what makes it worse
 
Is you just play the golden boy
And got so lost in all the noise of
“You’re kind, and you’re so perfect” 
“I’d love to be your girlfriend”
 
How’s life living on the surface?
You can really play the part
While you stay breaking all these hearts 
Oh “what’s it like to be his girlfriend”
Looks good but it’s a burden
You were lucky once
Have fun living on the surface

Music video by Freya Skye performing golden boy.© 2026 Hollywood Records, Inc.

snippet.title: W Sound 23 “5 Estrellas” - Myke Towers, Westcol, Ovy On The Drums
snippet.description:
Stream Aqui:  https://wml.link/5Estrellas-WSound23-WSoundxMykeTowersxOvyOnTheDrums
✅ Siguenos en las Redes: ‪ @wsoundwestcol   
Instagram -   www.instagram.com/westcol  
                        www.instagram.com/ovyonthedrums    
                        www.instagram.com/myketowers
Letra 

INTRO / TAG

E-e-e… encima tuyo no sé cómo acabé.
O-O-Ovy on the Drums…
Young Kingz, baby.

⸻

PRE-CORO

Pensaba que no la volvería a ver,
pero aquí de frente la tengo otra vez.
Encima tuyo no sé cómo acabé.
Siempre que usted quiera, déjeme saber.
En el cinco estrellas yo la enamoré,
el universo la puse a ver.
Si me insiste… la raya cruzaré.
Si me enchulo, de paso excúsame…

⸻

VERSO 1

Es que cualquiera se enamora…
Ella al gimnasio le llega a primera hora.
Se viste ALO, pero ni les dice “hola”.
Yo quiero devorarte… sin mucha demora,

sin mucha demora.
Ella no se ajora,
si hoy no fue bien, mañana mejora.
Te pienso oyendo a Ricardo Arjona…
¿dónde estará metida mi nalgona?

A veces me desespero porque
me pongo a pensar que ella está con quién…
Empezó a bailar y no la solté,
yo la voy a rankear, está en el top ten.

No se puso el sostén…
mami, tú burlas cualquier “retén”.
Está soltera y ellos no le creen.
Westcol, ¿dónde están las mujeres?
Yo le llego donde estén.

⸻

CORO

Pensaba que no la volvería a ver,
pero aquí de frente la tengo otra vez.
Encima tuyo no sé cómo acabé.
Siempre que usted quiera, déjeme saber.
En el cinco estrellas yo la enamoré,
el universo la puse a ver.
Si me insiste… la raya cruzaré.
Si me enchulo, de paso excúsame…

⸻

OUTRO / TALK

Mami chula, no te pierdas…
Me olvido cuando me acostaba en tu entrepierna.
Cualquiera cae con esa carita tierna.
Del centro comercial, le compro todas las tiendas,
porque tú eres la favorita mía.

Yo de noche y de día,
a cualquier hora la pienso,
no supe que vendría.

Myke Towers, baby…
E-e-e… Ovy on the Drums…
W Sound.

⸻

PART 2 — VERSO 2 (RAP / FLEX)

(Young Kingz, baby)
Parece una W el logo de la Maserati…

E-e-esta es la W Sound,
aquí vo’a tirar un par de flows que no había usa’o.
Se dice que estoy alza’o,
porque me sale muy fácil y ellos se ven forza’o.

Se quedaron estanca’o, yo les pasé zafa’o,
contando money me amanezco.
Tírale a Ovy y Westcol…
vámonos pa’ Guatapé con los bote’ y los jetsko.

Hay como 5.000 cancione’ por si un día envejezco,
esta vida de lujo a veces siento que ni la merezco.
En la suite presidencial, en los hoteles cinco estrella’,
los chef de Michelin… en la costilla un par de estrella’.

Mis diablas, después de que los seducen, los estrellan…
Mis locos los andan buscando pero no se entregan…


© 2026 W Sound/Big Ligas

snippet.title: The Kingdom is Within You
snippet.description:
all around you
plates are spinning
life is a game
nobody's winning

nothing is simple
it ain't black and white
it's a circus of shadows
all the way to the light

I don't wanna offend you
I never intend to
the kingdom is within you

I have bought every pain
I ever want to feel
nothing is hidden
all will be revealed

yea the more that you're right
the more that you're wrong
life is so short
but the days are so long

I've only borrowed
what I can lend you
the kingdom is within you

and round and round and round and round and round you
confusion
and round and round and round and round and round you
illusion

when we've been here 10,000 years
and nothing's ever seemed so clear
what's keeping you
from being near you?
the kingdom is within you

over the deserts
over the plains
I have come from afar
just to be here again

I'm as old as the mountain
I'm as young as a child
my soul's gonna set
like a sun with a smile

scream at the sky
no one can hear you
the kingdom is within you

and round and round and round and round and round you
confusion
and round and round and round and round and round you
illusion

when we've been here 10,000 years
and nothing's ever seemed so clear
what's keeping you
from being near you?
the kingdom is within you

snippet.description:
The Netflix series "BAKI-DOU: The Invincible Samurai" starts streaming worldwide on Thursday, February 26, 2026, only on Netflix.
https://www.netflix.com/bakidou

Musashi Miyamoto — the ultimate symbol of strength — descends into an underground fighting arena where the use of weapons is permitted. Underground fighters including Doppo Orochi, Goki Shibukawa and Sea King Retsu square off in succession against Musashi and his godlike strength. It’s sword versus fist in the most heart-pounding and deadly battles yet, where defeat means certain death.
Be prepared to be blown away by Baki and the other underground fighters as they bravely take on this new battle to determine the strongest fighter in human history.

Do I let our love die
When you’re the only other keeper
Of my most precious memories


Yeah
I’ve been drinking

I can’t call you ‘bout you and me?


‘Cause I’ll do anything

Such magic places

But now

Watching all the cars passing by
Like a kid waiting for my ride


I’ll do anything 
For you to love me again
If you don’t like me now
I will change for you 
I’ll change for you
